data.description: Welcome to the epitome of metropolitan living in this stunning 4-bed, 3-bath condo, where sophistication meets comfort. Nestled in the heart of Omaha, this exclusive residence redefines urban living with its contemporary design, spacious & open floor plan that seamlessly connects living, dining, & kitchen areas. The expansive windows allow natural light to flood the space, creating an inviting atmosphere. Featuring four generously sized bedrooms with ample space for rest & rejuvenation. Master suite is a sanctuary, boasting a balcony, breathtaking lighting & a spacious walk-in closet. Additional bedrooms are thoughtfully designed with its own unique character & charm. Located near Blackstone, UNMC, & Midtown, this condo allows residents to enjoy the vibrant energy of the city while maintaining a sense of privacy & tranquility. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite condo your new home. Schedule a viewing today & experience the epitome of sophisticated urban living.
